<div class="tabs">
    <div class="tab">
        <button id ="sign-up-helper" class="tablinks active">How to start helping</button>
        <button id ="request-help-helper" class="tablinks">How to request help</button>
    </div>
    <div id="sign-up-helper-content" class="sm6 tabcontent active">
        <h2>New to volunteer with HelpMyStreet:</h2>
        <p>
            Help as much or as little as you like with our easy to use platform. We show you where help is needed near you so you can help in a way that’s right for you.
        </p>
        <div class="sm1"><span class="fab circle">1</span></div>
        <div class="sm7">
            <h4>
                Register with us
            </h4>
            <p>
                Sign up using the green button below.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="sm1"><span class="fab circle">2</span></div>
        <div class="sm7">
            <h4>
                Verify your ID
            </h4>
            <p>
                Verifying your ID is quick and easy and lets us know you’re a real person! All you need is valid photo ID and a mobile device.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="sm1"><span class="fab circle">3</span></div>
        <div class="sm7">
            <h4>
                Find and accept requests for help
            </h4>
            <p>
                Browse open requests in your profile and accept the ones you can help with.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="sm1"><span class="fab circle">4</span></div>
        <div class="sm7">
            <h4>
                Help those in need
            </h4>
            <p>
                Get in touch and let them know when you’ll be there to help!
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="sm1"><span class="fab circle">5</span></div>
        <div class="sm7">
            <h4>
                Come back for more!
            </h4>
            <p>
                Don’t forget to keep checking back for new requests near you!
            </p>
        </div>
        <p>Find out more by checking out our <a href="/questions">FAQs</a></p>
        <div class="sm4">
            <a href="/account" class="btn cta large fill mt16 btn--sign-up">Provide Help</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="request-help-helper-content" class="sm6 tabcontent inactive">
        <h2>How to request help:</h2>
        <p>
            We protect your privacy by only sharing your details with the people who need them, when they need them.
        </p>
        <div class="sm1"><span class="fab circle">1</span></div>
        <div class="sm7">
            <h4>
                Tell us what you need
            </h4>
            <p>
                Request help using the orange button below - you can request help for yourself, or for someone else like a loved one at the other end of the country.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="sm1"><span class="fab circle">2</span></div>
        <div class="sm7">
            <h4>
                Wait for a volunteer to get in touch
            </h4>
            <p>
                As soon as a volunteer accepts your request we’ll let you know!
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="sm1"><span class="fab circle">3</span></div>
        <div class="sm7">
            <h4>
                Receive the help you need
            </h4>
            <p>
                Volunteers offer their time and skills for free, but if your volunteer incurs any costs you need to pay back (like the cost of your groceries for example) they’ll let you know how you can pay them back.
            </p>
        </div>
        <p>Find out more by checking out our <a href="/questions">FAQs</a></p>
        <div class="sm4">
            <a href="/request-help" class="btn cta large fill mt16 btn--request-help cta--orange">Request Help</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>